      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Air Conditioner Structure Description - Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "indoor"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The air conditioner uses an air-mix system."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The heater unit consists of a heater core and evaporator, and is equipped with an air mix damper and outlet switching damper."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The blower unit is equipped with a blower motor, inside/outside air switching damper, and A/C filter, and is connected to the heater unit by a duct integrated with the unit."
    },
